{"word":"ζωοποιέω","slug":"ζωοποιέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ζωοποιέω</el></b> [<el>ζωός</el> ‘alive’, <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ποιέω\">ποιέω</a></el>] ‘cause to be alive’, <b>make alive, give life to,</b> in general <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on existence transcending the merely physical <b><a href='B:500 5:21'>J 5:21</a>; <a href='B:500 6:63'>6:63</a>; <a href='B:520 4:17'>Ro 4:17</a>; <a href='B:520 8:11'>8:11</a>; <a href='B:530 15:22'>1 Cor 15:22</a>, <a href='B:530 15:36'>36</a>, <a href='B:530 15:45'>45</a>; <a href='B:540 3:6'>2 Cor 3:6</a>; <a href='B:550 3:21'>Gal 3:21</a>; <a href='B:610 6:13'>1 Ti 6:13</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:670 3:18'>1 Pt 3:18</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ζῷον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ζῶσαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}